## Design Guidelines

CRITICAL: Read DESIGN_GUIDELINES.md in project root before building any section component

Saisei-inspired design system with these priorities:

1. Grand scale typography (text-7xl for hero, text-6xl for sections)
2. Generous spacing (py-24 sections, py-32 hero)
3. Theme colors ONLY (never hardcode hex values)
4. Phased animation approach (structure Week 2, motion Week 3)

Key spacing values:

- Section vertical: py-16 mobile, py-20 tablet, py-24 desktop
- Heading to body: mb-6
- Button groups: gap-4
- Card grids: gap-6 or gap-8

Typography hierarchy:

- Hero H1: text-5xl mobile → text-7xl desktop, font-serif, text-primary-gold
- Section H2: text-4xl mobile → text-6xl desktop, font-serif, text-primary-gold
- Body: text-base → text-lg, font-sans, text-accent-white

Animation rules Week 2:

- NO animations during initial build
- Focus on layout, spacing, content structure
- Animations added in Week 3 polish phase

Animation rules Week 3:

- Use existing classes: animate-fade-in, animate-slide-up, animate-delay-X
- Use useIntersectionObserver for viewport entry
- Use useScrollPosition for parallax effects
- Only animate transform and opacity (GPU-accelerated)

Image requirements:

- Use loading="lazy" for below-fold images
- Use loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" for hero
- Implement blur placeholder while loading
- Grid images use group hover:scale-105 effect

Never hardcode colors examples:

- WRONG: text-[#D4AF37], style={{ color: '#d4af37' }}
- RIGHT: text-primary-gold, style={{ color: 'var(--color-primary-gold)' }}

Component building checklist with design:

- Use .section class for vertical spacing
- Use .container-custom for horizontal constraints
- Use .section-title for section headings
- Typography scale from guidelines
- Theme colors only
- Mobile-first responsive
- Accessibility maintained
- NO animations in Week 2
- Structure and spacing focus

Git commit rules:

- NEVER add AI signatures or references
- Write commits as if developer wrote them directly
- No "Built by Claude" anywhere

When building sections in Week 2:

- Focus ONLY on structure, layout, content
- Use correct spacing from guidelines
- Use typography scale from guidelines
- Use theme colors from guidelines
- Skip ALL animations and fancy effects
- Make it work first, polish later
